<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;CARVEDILOL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Carvedilol is a beta blocker medication used to treat conditions such as congestive heart failure and high blood pressure, sold under the brand name Coreg."&lt;SEP&gt;"Carvedilol is a drug used for the treatment of congestive heart failure, and its discovery was led by a researcher who holds a patent for its use."&lt;SEP&gt;"Carvedilol is a marketed product for which Robert R. Ruffolo, Jr holds the patent for the discovery of its use in treating congestive heart failure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Carvedilol is a non-specific Beta-adrenoceptor antagonist used in treating various conditions, including heart failure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c41ddd49edd0129b691f6bee9b953e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 128}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COREG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Coreg is the brand name for the medication Carvedilol, used to treat conditions such as congestive heart failure and high blood pressure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONGESTIVE HEART FAILURE (CHF)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Congestive Heart Failure (CHF) is a condition characterized by the heart's inability to pump enough blood to meet the body's needs, often treated with medications like Carvedilol."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 127}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LEFT VENTRICULAR DYSFUNCTION (LVD)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Left Ventricular Dysfunction (LVD) is a condition where the left ventricle of the heart does not contract effectively, often treated with Carvedilol after a heart attack."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 128}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIGH BLOOD PRESSURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"High Blood Pressure is a condition where the force of blood against the artery walls is too high, often treated with medications like Carvedilol."&lt;SEP&gt;"High Blood Pressure is a medical condition that Metolazone is used to treat."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 97}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CARDIAC ASTHMA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cardiac Asthma is a medical diagnosis of wheezing, coughing, or shortness of breath due to congestive heart failure, mimicking ordinary asthma."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 126}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEART FAILURE WITH PRESERVED EJECTION FRACTION (HFPEF)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Heart Failure with Preserved Ejection Fraction (HFpEF) is a form of congestive heart failure where the ejection fraction is greater than 50%, affecting approximately half of people with heart failure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 127}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEART FAILURE WITH REDUCED EJECTION FRACTION (HFREF)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Heart Failure with Reduced Ejection Fraction (HFrEF) is a form of congestive heart failure where the ejection fraction is less than 50%, affecting the remaining half of people with heart failure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 127}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TERRY'S NAILS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Terry's Nails is a physical condition characterized by white fingernails or toenails with a 'ground glass' appearance, often due to decreased vascularity and increased connective tissue in the nail bed."&lt;SEP&gt;"Terry's nails are characterized by a white appearance with a 'ground glass' appearance without lunula, often associated with decreased vascularity and increased connective tissue in the nail bed, and commonly seen in liver failure, cirrhosis, diabetes mellitus, congestive heart failure, hyperthyroidism, or malnutrition."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WHEEZING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Wheezing is a symptom of Cardiac Asthma, characterized by a whistling sound during breathing."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 126}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;COUGHING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Coughing is a symptom of Cardiac Asthma, often associated with wheezing and shortness of breath."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 126}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SHORTNESS OF BREATH&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Shortness of Breath is a symptom of Cardiac Asthma, often experienced alongside wheezing and coughing."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 126}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ELDERLY PATIENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Elderly Patients are a demographic group where one-third of congestive heart failure cases include Cardiac Asthma."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 98}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 126}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VASCULARITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vascularity refers to the presence and distribution of blood vessels, which is decreased in Terry's Nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONNECTIVE TISSUE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Connective Tissue is increased in the nail bed of Terry's Nails, contributing to its characteristic appearance."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d42c73cf1e34557089cd51fc812ce189</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONGESTIVE HEPATOPATHY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DISEASE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Congestive hepatopathy, also known as nutmeg liver and chronic passive congestion of the liver, is liver dysfunction due to venous congestion, usually due to congestive heart failure. It is characterized by a 'speckled' appearance of the liver, with dark spots representing the dilated and congested hepatic venules and small hepatic veins, and paler areas representing unaffected surrounding liver tissue."&lt;SEP&gt;"Congestive hepatopathy, also known as nutmeg liver, is a form of liver dysfunction caused by venous congestion, typically due to congestive heart failure. It is characterized by a 'speckled' appearance of the liver, with dark spots representing dilated and congested hepatic venules and small hepatic veins, and paler areas representing unaffected liver tissue."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LIVER FAILURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Liver failure is a serious medical condition where the liver is unable to function properly, often leading to the development of Terry's nails and other systemic symptoms."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CIRRHOSIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cirrhosis is a late-stage liver disease characterized by scarring and the formation of regenerative nodules, often resulting from long-term liver damage and associated with Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DIABETES MELLITUS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Diabetes mellitus is a metabolic disorder characterized by high blood sugar levels, which can contribute to the development of Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONGESTIVE HEART FAILURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Congestive Heart Failure is a medical condition that Metolazone is used to treat."&lt;SEP&gt;"Congestive Heart Failure is a medical condition treated by drugs such as carvedilol and ibopamine."&lt;SEP&gt;"Congestive Heart Failure is a specific type of heart failure where fluid accumulates in the lungs and other parts of the body, often due to poor left ventricular function."&lt;SEP&gt;"Congestive heart failure is a condition where the heart cannot pump enough blood to meet the body's needs, leading to venous congestion and the development of Terry's nails and other signs of congestive hepatopathy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c41ddd49edd0129b691f6bee9b953e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 100}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HYPERTHYROIDISM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hyperthyroidism is a condition where the thyroid gland produces too much thyroid hormone, which can affect the liver and lead to the development of Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MALNUTRITION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Malnutrition is a state of insufficient intake or absorption of calories and nutrients, which can affect the liver and lead to the development of Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;KIDNEY FAILURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Kidney failure is a condition where the kidneys are unable to filter waste products from the blood effectively, and it can sometimes be associated with the development of Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 101}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;NUTMEG LIVER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DISEASE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Nutmeg liver, also known as congestive hepatopathy, is a condition where the liver appears 'speckled' like a grated nutmeg kernel due to chronic passive congestion, usually caused by congestive heart failure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 100}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CHRONIC PASSIVE CONGESTION OF THE LIVER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Chronic passive congestion of the liver is a condition where the liver becomes congested due to venous obstruction, leading to a 'speckled' appearance and other symptoms."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 100}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FIBROSIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Fibrosis is a condition where excessive scar tissue forms in the liver, often as a result of prolonged congestion and can occur in severe cases of congestive hepatopathy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 100}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CARDIAC CIRRHOSIS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DISEASE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cardiac Cirrhosis is a specific type of liver scarring caused by right heart failure, resulting from hepatic congestion."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cardiac cirrhosis is a type of liver cirrhosis that results from right heart failure, leading to chronic passive congestion and the development of characteristic liver pathology."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 100}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BETA-3 ADRENERGIC ANTAGONIST&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DRUG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Beta-3 Adrenergic Antagonist is a type of adrenergic antagonist that blocks Beta-3 adrenergic receptors, used in medical treatments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beta-3 adrenergic antagonist is a type of medication that acts on the beta-3 adrenergic receptors, often used in the treatment of certain conditions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VENOUS CONGESTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Venous congestion is a condition where there is an accumulation of blood in the veins, often leading to liver congestion and the development of Terry's nails."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEPATIC VENULES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ANATOMY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hepatic venules are small blood vessels in the liver that carry deoxygenated blood from the liver cells to the hepatic veins."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEPATIC VEINS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ANATOMY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hepatic veins are large blood vessels that carry deoxygenated blood from the liver to the inferior vena cava."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RIGHT HEART FAILURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Right Heart Failure is a condition where the right side of the heart is unable to pump blood effectively, leading to hepatic congestion and potentially cardiac cirrhosis."&lt;SEP&gt;"Right heart failure is a condition where the right side of the heart is unable to pump enough blood to the lungs, leading to venous congestion and the development of nutmeg liver."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INFERIOR VENA CAVA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ANATOMY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The inferior vena cava is a large vein that carries deoxygenated blood from the lower half of the body to the right atrium of the heart."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REGENERATIVE NODULES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ANATOMY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Regenerative nodules are areas of the liver where normal liver tissue is replaced by abnormal tissue, often seen in advanced liver disease such as cirrhosis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SCARRING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Scarring, or fibrosis, is a condition where excessive scar tissue forms in the liver, often as a result of prolonged congestion and can occur in severe cases of congestive hepatopathy."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SYSTEMIC DISEASES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DISEASE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Systemic diseases are diseases that affect the entire body, and the recognition of characteristic nail patterns, such as Terry’s nails, may be a helpful herald for early diagnosis of these diseases."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f86ff993e599cae86cfaceb5a776544a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEPATIC CONGESTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hepatic Congestion is a medical condition characterized by the accumulation of blood in the liver, which can lead to fibrosis."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;L-748,328&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DRUG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"L-748,328 is a specific Beta-3 adrenergic antagonist known for its high specificity in blocking Beta-3 adrenoceptors."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;L-748,337&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DRUG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"L-748,337 is another specific Beta-3 adrenergic antagonist with high specificity in blocking Beta-3 adrenoceptors."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SR 59,230A&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DRUG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"SR 59,230A is a specific Beta-3 adrenergic antagonist known for its high specificity in blocking Beta-3 adrenoceptors."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HEART FAILURE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Heart Failure is a medical condition where the heart cannot pump enough blood to meet the body's needs, often leading to symptoms such as shortness of breath and leg swelling."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;METOLAZONE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Metolazone is a thiazide-like diuretic used in treating conditions such as edema and hypertension."&lt;SEP&gt;"Metolazone is a thiazide-like diuretic used to treat medical conditions such as congestive heart failure and high blood pressure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 97}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ZYTANIX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"BRAND"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Zytanix is a brand name for Metolazone, marketed by Zydus Cadila."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ZAROXOLYN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Zaroxolyn is a brand name for Metolazone."&lt;SEP&gt;"Zaroxolyn is another brand name for the drug Metolazone, possibly marketed by a different organization."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 97}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MYKROX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mykrox is a brand name for Metolazone."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mykrox is yet another brand name for the drug Metolazone, possibly marketed by a different organization."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 19}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 97}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LIVER SCARRING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Liver Scarring, or fibrosis, is a condition where the liver tissue becomes thick and stiff, often due to chronic liver diseases."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BETA-3 ADRENERGIC RECEPTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"STRUCTURE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Beta-3 Adrenergic Receptors are specific types of adrenergic receptors that can be blocked by Beta-3 adrenergic antagonists."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;THIAZIDE-LIKE DIURETICS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Thiazide-Like Diuretics are a class of drugs used to treat conditions such as edema and hypertension, including Metolazone."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EDEMA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONDITION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Edema is a medical condition characterized by swelling due to excess fluid accumulation in the body tissues."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HYPERTENSION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Hypertension is a medical condition characterized by persistently elevated blood pressure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hypertension is a medical condition that Teveten is used for."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-27ed84b598c145c5643d08bc11ff8d99&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ef4d151671253ba277630ab09312d9a</data>
