<node id="&quot;LORETA JANETA VELÁZQUEZ&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Loreta Janeta Velázquez was a Cuban-born woman who served as a male Confederate soldier during the American Civil War, fighting in several battles before her gender was discovered. She later worked as a Confederate spy and became a double agent for the U.S. Secret Service. She died in 1923 under the name Loretta J. Beard at St. Elizabeths Hospital."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-71a19cc7327c229383d5efc7150544c8</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 9}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 59}]</data>
</node>
